TAILWIND


npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init -p

module.exports = {
  content: [
    "./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}",
  ],
  
index.css -
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;


update react scripts to latest

- npm install react-scripts@latest --- need this for old version of create react app, but if newly created react app, dont need this.

-- tailwind styling should work after this update on react-scripts.

TypeScript

1. install typescript and types => npm install --save typescript @types/node @types/react @types/react-dom @types/jest

2. create or initialize tsconfig =>  npx tsc --init

3. convert js files to ts

4. edit tsconfig

"jsx": "react-jsx",
"moduleResolution": "node", 

5. one by one fix errors and make app work

6. for type problems use FixMeLAter and go back to it after

export type FixMeLater = any;


**for errors when importing images,

create types dir in src, create index.d.ts then declare =>


declare module "*.jpg";
declare module "*.png";


find all FixMeLAter and fix hehe
